            "text": "<ul><li>Perfect for websites, publishers, bloggers, and creators looking for passive income. </li><li>Access to banners, links, and tracking tools. </li><li>Competitive commission rates on every sale you drive. </li><li>Flexible, promote as little or as often as suits you. </li></ul><p>Our Wave SUP Affiliate Program is managed through <strong>AWIN</strong>.</p><p>To Join please visit <a href=\"https://ui.awin.com/merchant-profile/36890?utm_source=affiliate-toolkit\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://ui.awin.com/merchant-profile/36890?utm_source=affiliate-toolkit\">AWIN</a></p>",
